(Jade and Gemstone Market)

3
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:41,560
Song En,

4
00:00:41,640 --> 00:00:42,679
you know what?

5
00:00:42,799 --> 00:00:44,960
This is indeed the cream of the crop!

6
00:00:44,960 --> 00:00:46,479
This will definitely

7
00:00:46,479 --> 00:00:49,079
make your money worthwhile.

8
00:00:49,080 --> 00:00:51,070
I've been in the gemstone market
for years myself,

9
00:00:51,100 --> 00:00:52,680
and I have never seen such fine quality.

10
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:54,980
I believe it's worth
at least three times its price.

11
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:56,759
Do you want to cut it open?

12
00:00:57,240 --> 00:00:57,719
Open it!

13
00:00:57,759 --> 00:00:58,280
Do you?

14
00:00:58,280 --> 00:01:16,239
- Open it!
- Open it!

